'''甲基丙烯酸钠'''是一种钠的羧酸盐，化学式为C<sub>4</sub>H<sub>5</sub>O<sub>2</sub>Na。它可由[[甲基丙烯酸|甲基丙烯酸]]和[[碳酸氢钠|碳酸氢钠]]<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of Polymer Research|volume=12|issue=5|language=en|issn=1022-9760|date=2005-10|pages=421–428|doi=10.1007/s10965-005-3323-y|url=http://link.springer.com/10.1007/s10965-005-3323-y|title=Lead Removal from Wastewater Using Cu(II) Polymethacrylate Formed by Gamma Radiation|accessdate=2020-08-25|author=C. Barrera-Díaz, M. Palomar-Pardavé, M. Romero-Romo, F. Ureña-Nuñez}}</ref>或[[氢氧化钠|氢氧化钠]]<ref>Dontsov, A. A.; Mikhlin, V. E.; Dogadkin, B. A. Vulcanization of elastomers by salts of methacrylic acid. ''Kauchuk i Rezina'', 1967. 26 (1): 20-22. ISSN: 0022-9466.</ref>反应得到。它可以用于制备其它甲基丙烯酸盐，如和[[氯化锌|氯化锌]]反应，得到甲基丙烯酸锌。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Radiation Physics and Chemistry|volume=111|language=en|date=2015-06|pages=67–73|doi=10.1016/j.radphyschem.2015.02.008|url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0969806X15000626|title=Electron paramagnetic resonance (EPR) study of free radicals in irradiated zinc poly methacrylate|accessdate=2020-08-25|author=S. Galindo, F. Ureña-Núñez|archive-date=2018-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180622051604/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0969806X15000626|dead-url=no}}</ref>它也可用于制备甲基丙烯酸酯。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Monatshefte für Chemie - Chemical Monthly|volume=140|issue=4|language=en|issn=0026-9247|date=2009-04|pages=413–422|doi=10.1007/s00706-008-0045-y|url=http://link.springer.com/10.1007/s00706-008-0045-y|title=Synthesis of methacrylate-functionalized phosphonates and phosphates with long alkyl-chain spacers and their self-aggregation in aqueous solutions|accessdate=2020-08-25|author=Denisa Francová, Guido Kickelbick}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|journal=Macromolecules|volume=49|issue=2|language=en|issn=0024-9297|date=2016-01-26|pages=445–454|doi=10.1021/acs.macromol.5b02142|url=https://pubs.acs.org/doi/10.1021/acs.macromol.5b02142|title=Cyclopolymerization of Disiloxane-Tethered 